 or all of our analyses compare with the numbers of units we identified in the following publicly available national datasets:</span></li></ol><ul type="disc" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:12pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 28.37pt; padding-left:7.48pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">Homes and Communities Agency’s annual Statistical Data Release (SDR)</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt"> which includes some informati</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">on on supported housing and on housing for older people (HOP)</span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:12pt; margin:0pt 0pt 6pt 28.37pt; padding-left:7.48pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">Elderly Accommodation Counsel (EAC)’s database of specialist housing for older people.</span></li></ul><table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; margin-left:30.6pt; width:457.5pt"><tr style="height:51.75pt"><td style="border-bottom-color:#000000; border-bottom-style:solid; border-bottom-width:1pt; border-left-color:#000000; border-left-style:solid; border-left-width:1pt; border-right-color:#000000; border-right-style:solid; border-right-width:1pt; border-top-color:#000000; border-top-style:solid; border-top-width:1pt; padding-left:5.4pt; padding-right:5.4pt; vertical-align:bottom; width:43.3pt"><p style="margin:6pt 0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">&#xa0;</span></p></td><td style="border-bottom-color:#000000; border-bottom-style:solid; border-bottom-width:1pt; border-right-color:#000000; border-right-style:solid; border-right-width:1pt; border-top-color:#000000; border-top-style:solid; border-top-width:1pt; padding-left:5.4pt; padding-right:5.4pt; vertical-align:bottom; width:70.85pt"><p style="margin:6pt 0pt; text-align:right"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">SDR supported units</spa